  40           * -# TIMER01_MODE3  Mode 3, TL0 as 8-bit Timer/Counter (controlled by TIMER0), TH0 as 8-bit Timer/Counter
             - (controlled
  41           * by TIMER1)
  42           * @param[in] u8gate Gate control
  43           * -# TIMER01_TR_GATE:    Starts counting when TCON.TR1 is set to 1
  44           * -# TIMER01_INT_TR_GATE:Starts counting when both INT1 and TR1 are set to 1
  45           * @param[in] u8cnt Clock source selection
  46           * -# TIMER01_ICLK: As Timer1, the driving clock is from the internal clock input
